	In a rich and unique multimedia experience, BEYOND VAN GOGH breaks the confines of the frame, allowing you to become fully immersed in a world larger than life. Explore Vincent's universe through a shareable and spirited 360° projection environment, where you can virtually feel the paint being applied to the digital canvas. Wielding colour and light, Van Gogh transformed hardship and darkness into brightness and joy, infusing his work with a contagious sense of hope that still rings true today. The soundscape is a collage of contemporary music with subtle sound effects bridging the gap between artwork and music, reflecting a truly multisensory experience of Vincent's life and works.
""";
