<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/68401ANKJDRLSGLSHHGCVSLLNTTTQRLMS> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Fire, Feathers & Flight  ";
  schema:description """
	PRE-CONCERT TALK 6:30PM   CONCERT 7:30PM  <span><br/></span>GUEST CONDUCTOR: Andrew Crust<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This concert opens with a bright and agile work that captures the quick moving sparkle and unpredictability of wild birds, then dives into dramatic storytelling, full of energy and contrast, all building toward a triumphant closing - one of the most uplifting movements in the symphonic repertoire and fitting for a season finale!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Programme:<span><br/></span>MORLOCK: Oiseaux bleus et sauvages (Wild Bluebirds)<span><br/></span>STRAVINSKY: Firebird Suite<span><br/></span>SIBELIUS: Symphony No. 2 in D Major, Op. 43<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Read more about the Vancouver Island Symphony, Guest Artists and the music at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vancouverislandsymphony.com\"> www.vancouverislandsymphony.com</a> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Driven by Passion. United in Sound</span><span><br/></span>Stay updated on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanislesymphony\"> Facebook</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vancouverislandsymphony/\"> Instagram</a><span><br/></span>
""";
