<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/45801APJPHDJMJCSGNSRNCNRNHDDTHVGL> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "FLEETWOOD MAGIC";
  schema:description """
	Fleetwood Magic, The Authentic Tribute to Fleetwood Mac, is more than a tribute—it’s a time machine. Known for their authentic recreation of Fleetwood Mac’s sound, style, and onstage chemistry, the band delivers a spellbinding journey through the legendary group’s greatest hits from the 60s through the 80s. <span><br/></span>  <span><br/></span>Dressed in vintage costumes and playing with period-correct instrument sounds, the band channels the magic of the Rock and Roll Hall of Famers with stunning precision. The crowd can expect to be transported by faithful renditions of timeless classics like \"Rhiannon\", \"Dreams\", \"Go Your Own Way\", \"Say You Love Me\" and many more. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The band’s soaring vocals and captivating stage presence have led to sold-out shows across the country, and their fanbase continues to grow with each performance. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you're a lifelong fan of The Mac or discovering their music for the first time, Fleetwood Magic promises a nostalgic and electric evening of music, memories, and magic. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Let the “Rumours” be true—Fleetwood Magic really does deliver the magic. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information about Fleetwood Magic, please visit: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.fleetwoodmagic.ca\">www.fleetwoodmagic.ca</a>
""";
