<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/70801ACCPCJTVQVGBDPKMJGLRTJJDDVBG> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Homeward Bound - Tickets available at Door";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Tickets available at Door</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">@St. Andrew's Presbyterian Church<span><br/></span>4235 Departure Bay Rd, Nanaimo, BC V9T 1C9</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Homeward Bound features the rich baritone/bass voice of <span class=\"BoldText\">Liam Robertson</span> in concert with selections from opera and musical theatre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Originally a native of Nanaimo, Liam has gone on to acquire a Master’s degree in opera performance from U.B.C. and he has since performed with Burnaby Lyric Opera, the Vancouver Opera and The Vancouver Symphony. Liam will be joined by <span class=\"BoldText\">The Sinclair Singers</span>, an excellent group of young talented vocalists. This concert promises to be a wonderful evening of musical delights and not to be missed!  
""";
