<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/70201ADHVPVLHCVCVCTRPRPPPJCCSKTGL> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "HULLABALOO";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Join Us for the 2nd Annual Nico Rhodes’ Hullabaloo!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready for an exhilarating night that promises not just a concert, but a <span class=\"BoldText\">joyful explosion of musical madness</span>! This is an event you won't want to miss!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Featuring the amazing <span class=\"BoldText\">Hullabaloo Chorus</span> with over <span class=\"BoldText\">100 singers</span> and the sensational <span class=\"BoldText\">Hullabaloo Band</span> - a powerhouse collective of some of the finest musicians from Vancouver Island! This year, we are thrilled to present a lineup of incredible artists including the beloved <span class=\"BoldText\">Fred Penner</span>, the captivating <span class=\"BoldText\">Joëlle Rabu</span>, the talented <span class=\"BoldText\">Ty Koch</span>, the enchanting <span class=\"BoldText\">Lilu Scott</span>, the mesmerizing <span class=\"BoldText\">Alexandria Maillot</span>, and the virtuoso <span class=\"BoldText\">Calvin Dyck</span> on violin!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Prepare to hear your favourite songs like never before! We’re taking hits from Classic Rock to Gospel and creatively reinventing them with bold, fresh arrangements, blending elements of <span class=\"BoldText\">Folk, Tango, Bluegrass, and Pop</span>. This musical fusion will lift your spirits, make you groove, and send chills down your spine! This night is a celebration designed for music lovers, joy-seekers, and anyone who believes in the magic of collective voices. So come and be part of the <span class=\"BoldText\">Hullabaloo</span>! Two Shows this year cause last year sold out!  <span class=\"BoldText\">We can’t wait to party with you!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Nico Rhodes, Artistic Director, Hullabaloo</span></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Nico</span> is a genre jumping, multilingual musician who is equally comfortable playing jazz, classical, funk or roots music, orchestrating a symphony and conducting choirs. He is in demand as a touring artist and has directed 40+ stage musicals to his credit. He has composed 400+ original compositions, and arranged two symphonic pops shows. Nico has been nominated for two Jessie and five Ovation Awards and in 2019 was honoured with Nanaimo’s Emerging Cultural Leader Award. Nico is the creator of the very popular Piano Heist shows.
""";
