<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/71801ABVJVLDBDPJBNLJVMTCQQRSJHMBM> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Kirkwood Dance Year End 2026";
  schema:description """
	Get ready for an unforgettable celebration of dance, talent, and community.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Kirkwood Academy of Performing Arts is excited to return to the Port Theatre stage with two incredible year-end performances.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From our tiniest baby ballerinas to our graduating Class of 2026, you’ll be inspired by the passion, artistry, and heart our dancers bring to the stage. Join us as we celebrate a full season of growth, creativity, and dedication - alongside our amazing Nanaimo arts community.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>• 12:00 PM Show: Ignite <span><br/></span>• 4:00 PM Show: Illuminate<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you're cheering on a first-time performer or a graduating dancer, these shows will be filled with energy, emotion, and unforgettable moments.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://facebook.com/kirkwoodacademy\"> facebook.com/kirkwoodacademy</a><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://instagram.com/kirkwoodacademy\"> instagram.com/kirkwoodacademy</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
