  schema:name "Menopause The Musical";
  schema:description """
	Menopause The Musical® - COME JOIN OUR SISTERHOOD!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Four women at a lingerie sale have nothing in common but a black lace bra AND memory loss, hot flashes, night sweats, not enough sex, too much sex and more! This hilarious musical parody set to classic tunes from the ‘60s, ‘70s and ‘80s will have you cheering and dancing in the aisles! See what more than 17 million women and fans worldwide have been laughing about for over 20 years!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It's the Hilarious Celebration of Women and The Change!®
""";
