<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/66601AGQCGDBVSBRBPDBPSKRTDHMKTVRL> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Mischief, Madness & Mystery ";
  schema:description """
	PRE-CONCERT TALK 6:30PM   CONCERT 7:30PM  <span><br/></span>GUEST CONDUCTOR: Daniel Bartholomew-Poyser<span><br/></span>GUEST ARTIST: Cameron Crozman, Cello <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Opening playfully and lightheartedly, this programme takes you on a vivid musical journey - spark to shadow, reflection to wit and surprise. We’re thrilled for the return of award winning cellist Cameron Crozman performing the beautiful Elgar Cello Concerto.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Programme: <span><br/></span>Jared MILLER: Teaser-Pleaser<span><br/></span>ELGAR: Cello Concerto in E minor, Op. 85<span><br/></span>WALLEN: Photography Movement #1<span><br/></span>SHOSTAKOVICH: Symphony 9, Op. 70<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Read more about the Vancouver Island Symphony, Guest Artists and the music at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vancouverislandsymphony.com\"> www.vancouverislandsymphony.com</a> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Driven by Passion. United in Sound</span><span><br/></span>Stay updated on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanislesymphony\"> Facebook</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vancouverislandsymphony/\"> Instagram</a>
""";
