<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/49201ADMHVCPDCGVCRJSKQMLVHNQNVVVH> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Nanaimo Beatlemania!";
  schema:description """
	Travel Through Time With The Beatles!<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>From the electrifying Ed Sullivan debut to the soul-stirring Let It Be, The Liverpool 4 takes you on a magical journey through every iconic era of The Beatles’ legendary career. Experience the unforgettable hits live on stage — delivered with the same energy, impeccable musicianship, showmanship, fun, and cheeky humour that made the Fab Four a global sensation.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>The Liverpool 4 — Canada’s Tribute to The Beatles — has been captivating audiences across North America for nearly 20 years. With thousands of shows under their belt, they've wowed crowds at venues like Maple Leaf Gardens, Massey Hall, Global TV’s Morning Show, and even Universal Pictures events — not to mention countless theatres and festivals coast to coast. This live concert features two sets with a 20-minute intermission. Whether you're singing along, dancing in the aisles, or just rattling your jewelry — you'll feel the magic of Beatlemania all over again.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>Come Together — and relive the greatest music ever made!<span><br/></span>
""";
