    schema:Event;
  schema:name "POPS: A Change is Gonna Come: A Night of Soul";
  schema:description """
	GUEST CONDUCTOR: Scott MacInnes<span><br/></span>GUEST ARTIST: Sonia Reid  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Love is in the air as the VIS and powerhouse vocalist Sonia Reid deliver a Valentine’s celebration inspired by the Queens of soul: Aretha Franklin, Whitney Houston and Tina Turner. From heart stopping ballads to electrifying anthems, these concerts are pure heart and soul.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Read more about the Vancouver Island Symphony, Guest Artists and the music at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vancouverislandsymphony.com\"> www.vancouverislandsymphony.com</a> Driven by Passion. United in Sound<span><br/></span>Stay updated on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanislesymphony\"> Facebook</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vancouverislandsymphony/\"> Instagram</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Multi show discounts available</span>; simply add the 3 POPS shows to your shopping cart to see your savings!</h2><span><br/></span>
""";
