<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/66801AQKPRHKKGQQBTMBVQVVTVMKKQTGN> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "POPS: Our Family & Friends Christmas with fraser+KEL";
  schema:description """
	GUEST CONDUCTOR: Herb Smith<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our Family & Friends Christmas features internationally renowned husband-and-wife duo fraser+KEL for a heartfelt symphonic holiday celebration! Fraser Walters is best known as co-founder of Universal Music's multi-platinum and JUNO-winning supergroup The Tenors, with whom he co-created five studio albums and performed in thousands of concerts and broadcasts worldwide. Kelly Elizabeth Levesque, who has had an international recording and performing profile since signing her first major-label record deal in her teens, has appeared as a soloist at iconic venues including Royal Albert Hall, the Sydney Opera House, The Kennedy Center, and Madison Square Garden with global legends such as Sting, Andrea Bocelli, Josh Groban, and Michael Bolton. Fraser and Kelly’s combined story began in 2009 in Chicago, where they met as featured performers on the North American leg of the David Foster & Friends global tour, led by the legendary producer and songwriter himself. Now, for the first time in their remarkable careers, Fraser and Kelly have joined forces as a writing, production, and performing team, blending soaring harmonies with lush orchestral arrangements. Together with the VIS they promise to ignite your Christmas spirit!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Read more about the Vancouver Island Symphony, Guest Artists and the music at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vancouverislandsymphony.com\"> www.vancouverislandsymphony.com</a> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Driven by Passion. United in Sound</span><span><br/></span>Stay updated on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vanislesymphony\"> Facebook</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vancouverislandsymphony/\"> Instagram</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Multi show discounts available</span>; simply add the 3 POPS shows to your shopping cart to see your savings!</h2>
""";
