<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/51201ANJTLKTPNSNHSSNGJHMCPQDDDKRV> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Relive the Music '50s, '60s & '70s";
  schema:description """
	Relive the Music 50s & 60s SHOW is back after 158 standing ovations in a row across Canada with a new twist.  We are keeping the biggest hits from the 50s & 60s, then adding the 70s - ROCK & DISCO MUSIC to our craziness, such as Bee Gees, ABBA, Queen, Chic, Meat Loaf, Eagles, Led Zeppelin, Earth, Wind & Fire, Donna Summer, Aerosmith, KC & the Sunshine Band and more.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It's like watching over two dozen Tribute Shows in one evening.   <span><br/></span>World Rock & Roll Champion, as seen twice on The Oprah Winfrey Show and The Ellen Show, Luisa Marshall will be performing all her magic alongside the other talented singers and the great band. Don’t miss this show.   <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A one-of-a-kind show that takes the audience through Music History, Trivia & Memories of the 50’s & 60’s, & 70s Rock and Disco Era. You will likely learn many things you never knew about these artists. You will see an energetic live band, amazing front singers, and dancers transforming and reliving three decades of music, costumes, trends, and dance, with video imagery in the background.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
