<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/78401AJTHVQKCLLSCNJNQLQTRRQHGJKMK> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "SPOTLIGHT: Winter Harp";
  schema:description """
	AN ENCHANTING CHRISTMAS TRADITION<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Welcome, Ye All. Believe it or not, Christmas is on its way, and <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Winter Harp</span></span> takes you into the heart of the season with a concert that will stir your soul. Expect tears and laughter as music, stories, and poems transport you to another land — a land filled with snow, Christmas, and memories of loved ones gathered together. Carols both rare and familiar will have your heart singing. Enjoy the sounds of harps, flute, violin, bass flute, medieval instruments, percussion, poetry, and song on a stage with a gorgeous cathedral backdrop and snow — this is Winter Harp.  Come with us as we journey deep into the heart of Christmas.
""";
